msgid ""
"\n"
"Plugin to make multiple ipa calls via one remote procedure call\n"
"\n"
"To run this code in the lite-server\n"
"\n"
"curl   -H \"Content-Type:application/json\"          -H \"Accept:application/"
"json\" -H \"Accept-Language:en\"        --negotiate -u :          --cacert /"
"etc/ipa/ca.crt           -d  @batch_request.json -X POST       http://"
"localhost:8888/ipa/json\n"
"\n"
"where the contents of the file batch_request.json follow the below example\n"
"\n"
"{\"method\":\"batch\",\"params\":[[\n"
"        {\"method\":\"group_find\",\"params\":[[],{}]},\n"
"        {\"method\":\"user_find\",\"params\":[[],{\"whoami\":\"true\","
"\"all\":\"true\"}]},\n"
"        {\"method\":\"user_show\",\"params\":[[\"admin\"],{\"all\":true}]}\n"
"        ],{}],\"id\":1}\n"
"\n"
"The format of the response is nested the same way.  At the top you will see\n"
"  \"error\": null,\n"
"    \"id\": 1,\n"
"    \"result\": {\n"
"        \"count\": 3,\n"
"            \"results\": [\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"And then a nested response for each IPA command method sent in the request\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Plugin för att göra flera ipa-anrop via ett fjärrproceduranrop\n"
"\n"
"För att köra den här koden i lite-servern\n"
"\n"
"curl -H \"Content-Type:application/json\" -H \"Accept:application/json\" -H "
"\"Accept-Language:en\" --negotiate -u : --cacert /etc/ipa/ca.crt -d "
"@batch_request.json -X POST http://localhost:8888/ipa/json\n"
"\n"
"där innehållet i filen batch_request.json följer nedanstående exempel\n"
"\n"
"{\"method\":\"batch\",\"params\":[[\n"
"        {\"method\":\"group_find\",\"params\":[[],{}]},\n"
"        {\"method\":\"user_find\",\"params\":[[],"
"{\"whoami\":\"true\",\"all\":\"true\"}]},\n"
"        {\"method\":\"user_show\",\"params\":[[\"admin\"],{\"all\":true}]}\n"
"        ],{}],\"id\":1}\n"
"\n"
"Svarets format är kapslat på samma sätt.  Längst upp ser du\n"
"  \"error\": null,\n"
"    \"id\": 1,\n"
"    \"result\": {\n"
"        \"count\": 3,\n"
"            \"resultat\": [\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Och sedan ett nästlat svar för varje IPA-kommandometod som skickas i "
"begäran\n"

msgid "Nested Methods to execute"
msgstr "Nästlade metoder att utföra"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Server configuration\n"
"\n"
"Manage the default values that IPA uses and some of its tuning parameters.\n"
"\n"
"NOTES:\n"
"\n"
"The password notification value (--pwdexpnotify) is stored here so it will\n"
"be replicated. It is not currently used to notify users in advance of an\n"
"expiring password.\n"
"\n"
"Some attributes are read-only, provided only for information purposes. "
"These\n"
"include:\n"
"\n"
"Certificate Subject base: the configured certificate subject base,\n"
"  e.g. O=EXAMPLE.COM.  This is configurable only at install time.\n"
"Password plug-in features: currently defines additional hashes that the\n"
"  password will generate (there may be other conditions).\n"
"\n"
"When setting the order list for mapping SELinux users you may need to\n"
"quote the value so it isn't interpreted by the shell.\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLES:\n"
"\n"
" Show basic server configuration:\n"
"   ipa config-show\n"
"\n"
" Show all configuration options:\n"
"   ipa config-show --all\n"
"\n"
" Change maximum username length to 99 characters:\n"
"   ipa config-mod --maxusername=99\n"
"\n"
" Increase default time and size limits for maximum IPA server search:\n"
"   ipa config-mod --searchtimelimit=10 --searchrecordslimit=2000\n"
"\n"
" Set default user e-mail domain:\n"
"   ipa config-mod --emaildomain=example.com\n"
"\n"
" Enable migration mode to make \"ipa migrate-ds\" command operational:\n"
"   ipa config-mod --enable-migration=TRUE\n"
"\n"
" Define SELinux user map order:\n"
"   ipa config-mod --ipaselinuxusermaporder='guest_u:s0$xguest_u:s0$user_u:s0-"
"s0:c0.c1023$staff_u:s0-s0:c0.c1023$unconfined_u:s0-s0:c0.c1023'\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Serverkonfiguration\n"
"\n"
"Hantera standardvärdena som IPA använder och några av dess "
"inställningsparametrar.\n"
"\n"
"OBS:\n"
"\n"
"Värdet för lösenordsmeddelande (--pwdexpnotify) lagras här så att det "
"replikeras.\n"
"Det används för närvarande inte för att meddela användare i förväg om ett "
"lösenord\n"
"som håller på att gå\n"
"\n"
"ut. Vissa attribut är skrivskyddade och tillhandahålls endast i "
"informationssyfte.\n"
"Dessa\n"
"\n"
"inkluderar: Certifikatets ämnesbas: den konfigurerade certifikatets\n"
"ämnesbas, t.ex. O=EXAMPLE.COM. Detta kan endast konfigureras vid\n"
"installationen. Lösenordsplugin-funktioner: definierar för närvarande "
"ytterligare\n"
"hashvärden som lösenordet kommer att generera (det kan finnas\n"
"\n"
"andra villkor). När du ställer in ordningslistan för mappning av SELinux-"
"användare\n"
"kan du behöva ange värdet inom citationstecken så att det\n"
"\n"
"inte tolkas\n"
"\n"
"av skalet. EXEMPEL: Visa grundläggande\n"
"serverkonfiguration:\n"
"\n"
"ipa config-show Visa alla\n"
"konfigurationsalternativ:\n"
"\n"
"ipa config-show --all Ändra maximal längd på användarnamn\n"
"till 99 tecken: ipa config-mod\n"
"\n"
"--maxusername=99 Öka standardtids- och storleksgränserna för maximal\n"
"IPA-serversökning: ipa config-mod --searchtimelimit=10 --"
"searchrecordslimit=2000\n"
"\n"
"Ställ in standarddomän för användares\n"
"e-post: ipa config-mod --emaildomain=example.com\n"
"\n"
"Aktivera migreringsläge för att göra kommandot \"ipa migrate-ds\" "
"operativt:\n"
"ipa config-mod --enable-migration=TRUE Definiera\n"
"\n"
"SELinux-användarkartordning: ipa\n"
"config-mod --ipaselinuxusermaporder='guest_u:s0$xguest_u:s0$user_u:s0-"
"s0:c0.c1023$staff_u:s0-s0:c0.c1023$unconfined_u:s0-s0:c0.c1023'\n"

