msgid ""
"\n"
"Entitlements\n"
"\n"
"Manage entitlements for client machines\n"
"\n"
"Entitlements can be managed either by registering with an entitlement\n"
"server with a username and password or by manually importing entitlement\n"
"certificates. An entitlement certificate contains embedded information\n"
"such as the product being entitled, the quantity and the validity dates.\n"
"\n"
"An entitlement server manages the number of client entitlements available.\n"
"To mark these entitlements as used by the IPA server you provide a quantity\n"
"and they are marked as consumed on the entitlement server.\n"
"\n"
" Register with an entitlement server:\n"
"   ipa entitle-register consumer\n"
"\n"
" Import an entitlement certificate:\n"
"   ipa entitle-import /home/user/ipaclient.pem\n"
"\n"
" Display current entitlements:\n"
"   ipa entitle-status\n"
"\n"
" Retrieve details on entitlement certificates:\n"
"   ipa entitle-get\n"
"\n"
" Consume some entitlements from the entitlement server:\n"
"   ipa entitle-consume 50\n"
"\n"
"The registration ID is a Unique Identifier (UUID). This ID will be\n"
"IMPORTED if you have used entitle-import.\n"
"\n"
"Changes to /etc/rhsm/rhsm.conf require a restart of the httpd service.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Rättigheter\n"
"\n"
"Hantera rättigheter för klientdatorer\n"
"\n"
"Rättigheter kan hanteras antingen genom att registrera sig hos en\n"
"rättighetsserver med ett användarnamn och lösenord eller genom att manuellt\n"
"importera rättighetscertifikat. Ett rättighetscertifikat innehåller\n"
"inbäddad information såsom vilken produkt som rättigheten gäller, kvantitet\n"
"\n"
"och giltighetsdatum. En rättighetsserver hanterar antalet tillgängliga\n"
"klienträttigheter. För att markera dessa rättigheter som använda av IPA-"
"servern\n"
"anger du en kvantitet och de markeras som förbrukade på\n"
"\n"
"rättighetsservern. Registrera dig hos\n"
"en rättighetsserver: ipa\n"
"\n"
"entitle-register consumer Importera\n"
"ett rättighetscertifikat: ipa entitle-import\n"
"\n"
"/home/user/ipaclient.pem Visa\n"
"aktuella rättigheter:\n"
"\n"
"ipa entitle-status Hämta information om\n"
"behörighetscertifikat:\n"
"\n"
"ipa entitle-get Använd några behörigheter från\n"
"behörighetsservern: ipa\n"
"\n"
"entitle-consume 50 Registrerings-ID är en unik identifierare (UUID).\n"
"Detta ID IMPORTERAS om du har använt\n"
"\n"
"entitle-import. Ändringar i /etc/rhsm/rhsm.conf kräver en omstart av\n"
"httpd-tjänsten.\n"

