msgstr "kommaseparerad lista över privilegier"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Self-service Permissions\n"
"\n"
"A permission enables fine-grained delegation of permissions. Access Control\n"
"Rules, or instructions (ACIs), grant permission to permissions to perform\n"
"given tasks such as adding a user, modifying a group, etc.\n"
"\n"
"A Self-service permission defines what an object can change in its own "
"entry.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLES:\n"
"\n"
" Add a self-service rule to allow users to manage their address:\n"
"   ipa selfservice-add --permissions=write --attrs=street,postalCode,l,c,st "
"\"Users manage their own address\"\n"
"\n"
" When managing the list of attributes you need to include all attributes\n"
" in the list, including existing ones. Add telephoneNumber to the list:\n"
"   ipa selfservice-mod --attrs=street,postalCode,l,c,st,telephoneNumber "
"\"Users manage their own address\"\n"
"\n"
" Display our updated rule:\n"
"   ipa selfservice-show \"Users manage their own address\"\n"
"\n"
" Delete a rule:\n"
"   ipa selfservice-del \"Users manage their own address\"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Självbetjäningsbehörigheter\n"
"\n"
"En behörighet möjliggör detaljerad delegering av behörigheter. "
"Åtkomstkontrollregler,\n"
"eller instruktioner (ACI), ger behörighet att utföra vissa uppgifter, såsom\n"
"att lägga till en användare, ändra en grupp etc. En\n"
"\n"
"självbetjäningsbehörighet definierar vad ett objekt kan ändra i sin egen "
"post.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"EXEMPEL:\n"
"\n"
"Lägg till en självbetjäningsregel för att låta användare hantera sin\n"
"adress: ipa selfservice-add --permissions=write --"
"attrs=street,postalCode,l,c,st \"Användare hanterar sin egen\n"
"\n"
"adress\" När du hanterar listan med attribut måste du inkludera alla "
"attribut\n"
"i listan, inklusive befintliga. Lägg till telefonnummer i listan: ipa\n"
"selfservice-mod --attrs=street,postalCode,l,c,st,telephoneNumber \"Användare "
"hanterar sin egen adress\" Visa\n"
"\n"
"vår uppdaterade regel: ipa\n"
"selfservice-show \"Användare hanterar sin egen adress\" Ta\n"
"\n"
"bort en regel:\n"
"ipa selfservice-del \"Användare hanterar sin egen adress\"\n"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Services\n"
"\n"
"A IPA service represents a service that runs on a host. The IPA service\n"
"record can store a Kerberos principal, an SSL certificate, or both.\n"
"\n"
"An IPA service can be managed directly from a machine, provided that\n"
"machine has been given the correct permission. This is true even for\n"
"machines other than the one the service is associated with. For example,\n"
"requesting an SSL certificate using the host service principal credentials\n"
"of the host. To manage a service using host credentials you need to\n"
"kinit as the host:\n"
"\n"
" # kinit -kt /etc/krb5.keytab host/ipa.example.com@EXAMPLE.COM\n"
"\n"
"Adding an IPA service allows the associated service to request an SSL\n"
"certificate or keytab, but this is performed as a separate step; they\n"
"are not produced as a result of adding the service.\n"
"\n"
"Only the public aspect of a certificate is stored in a service record;\n"
"the private key is not stored.\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLES:\n"
"\n"
" Add a new IPA service:\n"
"   ipa service-add HTTP/web.example.com\n"
"\n"
" Allow a host to manage an IPA service certificate:\n"
"   ipa service-add-host --hosts=web.example.com HTTP/web.example.com\n"
"   ipa role-add-member --hosts=web.example.com certadmin\n"
"\n"
" Override a default list of supported PAC types for the service:\n"
"   ipa service-mod HTTP/web.example.com --pac-type=MS-PAC\n"
"\n"
" Delete an IPA service:\n"
"   ipa service-del HTTP/web.example.com\n"
"\n"
" Find all IPA services associated with a host:\n"
"   ipa service-find web.example.com\n"
"\n"
" Find all HTTP services:\n"
"   ipa service-find HTTP\n"
"\n"
" Disable the service Kerberos key and SSL certificate:\n"
"   ipa service-disable HTTP/web.example.com\n"
"\n"
" Request a certificate for an IPA service:\n"
"   ipa cert-request --principal=HTTP/web.example.com example.csr\n"
"\n"
" Generate and retrieve a keytab for an IPA service:\n"
"   ipa-getkeytab -s ipa.example.com -p HTTP/web.example.com -k /etc/httpd/"
"httpd.keytab\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Tjänster\n"
"\n"
"En IPA-tjänst är en tjänst som körs på en värd. IPA-tjänstposten kan lagra\n"
"en Kerberos-principal, ett SSL-certifikat eller båda. En IPA-tjänst\n"
"\n"
"kan hanteras direkt från en maskin, förutsatt att maskinen har fått\n"
"rätt behörighet. Detta gäller även för andra maskiner än den som\n"
"tjänsten är kopplad till. Till exempel att begära ett SSL-certifikat med\n"
"hjälp av värdens tjänsteprincipala autentiseringsuppgifter. För att hantera\n"
"en tjänst med hjälp av värdens autentiseringsuppgifter måste du kinit\n"
"som värd: # kinit\n"
"\n"
"-kt /etc/krb5.keytab host/ipa.example.com@EXAMPLE.COM Genom att\n"
"\n"
"lägga till en IPA-tjänst kan den associerade tjänsten begära ett\n"
"SSL-certifikat eller keytab, men detta utförs som ett separat steg; de\n"
"skapas inte som ett resultat av att tjänsten läggs\n"
"\n"
"till. Endast den offentliga delen av ett certifikat lagras i en tjänstpost;\n"
"den privata nyckeln lagras inte.\n"
"\n"
"EXEMPEL:\n"
"\n"
"Lägg till en ny IPA-tjänst:\n"
"ipa service-add HTTP/web.example.com\n"
"\n"
"Tillåt en värd att hantera ett IPA-tjänstcertifikat:\n"
"ipa service-add-host --hosts=web.example.com HTTP/web.example.com ipa\n"
"role-add-member --hosts=web.example.com certadmin Åsidosätt\n"
"\n"
"en standardlista över PAC-typer som stöds för tjänsten: ipa\n"
"service-mod HTTP/web.example.com --pac-type=MS-PAC Ta bort\n"
"\n"
"en IPA-tjänst: ipa\n"
"service-del HTTP/web.example.com Hitta\n"
"\n"
"alla IPA-tjänster som är associerade med en värd:\n"
"ipa service-find web.example.com Hitta\n"
"\n"
"alla HTTP-tjänster: ipa\n"
"service-find HTTP Inaktivera\n"
"\n"
"tjänstens Kerberos-nyckel och SSL-certifikat: ipa\n"
"service-disable HTTP/web.example.com Begär\n"
"\n"
"ett certifikat för en IPA-tjänst: ipa\n"
"cert-request --principal=HTTP/web.example.com example.csr Generera\n"
"\n"
"och hämta en keytab för en IPA-tjänst: ipa-getkeytab\n"
"-s ipa.example.com -p HTTP/web.example.com -k /etc/httpd/httpd.keytab\n"

msgid ""
"Override default list of supported PAC types. Use 'NONE' to disable PAC "
"support for this service"
msgstr ""
"Åsidosätt standardlistan över PAC-typer som stöds. Använd 'NONE' för att "
"inaktivera PAC-stöd för denna tjänst"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Groups of Sudo Commands\n"
"\n"
"Manage groups of Sudo Commands.\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLES:\n"
"\n"
" Add a new Sudo Command Group:\n"
"   ipa sudocmdgroup-add --desc='administrators commands' admincmds\n"
"\n"
" Remove a Sudo Command Group:\n"
"   ipa sudocmdgroup-del admincmds\n"
"\n"
" Manage Sudo Command Group membership, commands:\n"
"   ipa sudocmdgroup-add-member --sudocmds=/usr/bin/less,/usr/bin/vim "
"admincmds\n"
"\n"
" Manage Sudo Command Group membership, commands:\n"
"   ipa group-remove-member --sudocmds=/usr/bin/less admincmds\n"
"\n"
" Show a Sudo Command Group:\n"
"   ipa group-show localadmins\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Grupper av Sudo-kommandon\n"
"\n"
"Hantera grupper av Sudo-kommandon.\n"
"\n"
"EXEMPEL:\n"
"\n"
"Lägg till en ny Sudo-kommandogrupp:\n"
"ipa sudocmdgroup-add --desc='administratörskommandon' admincmds Ta\n"
"\n"
"bort en Sudo-kommandogrupp: ipa\n"
"sudocmdgroup-del admincmds Hantera\n"
"\n"
"medlemskap i Sudo-kommandogrupper, kommandon: ipa\n"
"sudocmdgroup-add-member --sudocmds=/usr/bin/less,/usr/bin/vim admincmds "
"Hantera\n"
"\n"
"medlemskap i Sudo-kommandogrupper, kommandon: ipa\n"
"group-remove-member --sudocmds=/usr/bin/less admincmds Visa en\n"
"\n"
"Sudo-kommandogrupp: ipa\n"
"group-show localadmins\n"

