#: ipaserver/plugins/hbacsvc.py:28
msgid ""
"\n"
"HBAC Services\n"
"\n"
"The PAM services that HBAC can control access to. The name used here\n"
"must match the service name that PAM is evaluating.\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLES:\n"
"\n"
" Add a new HBAC service:\n"
"   ipa hbacsvc-add tftp\n"
"\n"
" Modify an existing HBAC service:\n"
"   ipa hbacsvc-mod --desc=\"TFTP service\" tftp\n"
"\n"
" Search for HBAC services. This example will return two results, the FTP\n"
" service and the newly-added tftp service:\n"
"   ipa hbacsvc-find ftp\n"
"\n"
" Delete an HBAC service:\n"
"   ipa hbacsvc-del tftp\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"HBAC-tjänster\n"
"\n"
"De PAM-tjänster som HBAC kan kontrollera åtkomsten till. Namnet som\n"
"används här måste matcha det tjänstenamn som PAM\n"
"\n"
"utvärderar.\n"
"\n"
"EXEMPEL: Lägg till en ny\n"
"HBAC-tjänst: ipa hbacsvc-add\n"
"\n"
"tftp Ändra en befintlig HBAC-tjänst:\n"
"ipa hbacsvc-mod --desc=\"TFTP-tjänst\" tftp Sök\n"
"\n"
"efter HBAC-tjänster. Det här exemplet ger två resultat, FTP-tjänsten och\n"
"den nyligen tillagda tftp-tjänsten: ipa\n"
"hbacsvc-find ftp Ta bort\n"
"\n"
"en HBAC-tjänst: ipa\n"
"hbacsvc-del tftp\n"
"\n"

