msgid ""
"\n"
"Kerberos PKINIT feature status reporting tools.\n"
"\n"
"Report IPA masters on which Kerberos PKINIT is enabled or disabled\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLES:\n"
" List PKINIT status on all masters:\n"
"   ipa pkinit-status\n"
"\n"
