#: ipaserver/plugins/whoami.py:15
msgid ""
"\n"
"Return information about currently authenticated identity\n"
"\n"
"Who am I command returns information on how to get\n"
"more details about the identity authenticated for this\n"
"request. The information includes:\n"
"\n"
" * type of object\n"
" * command to retrieve details of the object\n"
" * arguments and options to pass to the command\n"
"\n"
"The information is returned as a dictionary. Examples below use\n"
"'key: value' output for illustrative purposes.\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLES:\n"
"\n"
" Look up as IPA user:\n"
"   kinit admin\n"
"   ipa console\n"
"   >> api.Command.whoami()\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
"   object: user\n"
"   command: user_show/1\n"
"   arguments: admin\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
" Look up as a user from a trusted domain:\n"
"   kinit user@AD.DOMAIN\n"
"   ipa console\n"
"   >> api.Command.whoami()\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
"   object: idoverrideuser\n"
"   command: idoverrideuser_show/1\n"
"   arguments: ('default trust view', 'user@ad.domain')\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
" Look up as a host:\n"
"   kinit -k\n"
"   ipa console\n"
"   >> api.Command.whoami()\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
"   object: host\n"
"   command: host_show/1\n"
"   arguments: ipa.example.com\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
" Look up as a Kerberos service:\n"
"   kinit -k -t /path/to/keytab HTTP/ipa.example.com\n"
"   ipa console\n"
"   >> api.Command.whoami()\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
"   object: service\n"
"   command: service_show/1\n"
"   arguments: HTTP/ipa.example.com\n"
"   ------------------------------------------\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Returnera information om aktuell autentiserad identitet\n"
"\n"
"Kommandot Who am I returnerar information om hur\n"
"man får mer detaljer om den identitet som autentiserats\n"
"för denna begäran. Informationen\n"
"\n"
"inkluderar: * typ\n"
"av objekt * kommando för att hämta detaljer\n"
"om objektet * argument och alternativ som ska\n"
"\n"
"skickas till kommandot Informationen returneras som en ordlista.\n"
"Exemplen nedan använder utdata av typen ”nyckel:\n"
"\n"
"värde” i\n"
"\n"
"illustrativt syfte.\n"
"EXEMPEL: Sök\n"
"som IPA-användare:\n"
"kinit admin ipa console >>\n"
"api.Command.whoami() ------------------------------------------\n"
"objekt: användare\n"
"kommando: user_show/1\n"
"argument: admin\n"
"------------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Sök som användare från en betrodd domän:\n"
"kinit user@AD.DOMAIN ipa\n"
"console >>\n"
"api.Command.whoami()\n"
"------------------------------------------\n"
"objekt: idoverrideuser\n"
"kommando: idoverrideuser_show/1\n"
"argument: ('standardförtroendevy', 'user@ad.domain')\n"
"------------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Sök som värd: kinit\n"
"-k ipa-konsol\n"
">> api.Command.whoami()\n"
"------------------------------------------\n"
"objekt: värd kommando: host_show/1 argument:\n"
"ipa.example.com\n"
"------------------------------------------\n"
"Sök som en Kerberos-tjänst:\n"
"kinit -k -t /path/to/keytab HTTP/ipa.example.com\n"
"\n"
"ipa console >> api.Command.whoami()\n"
"------------------------------------------ objekt:\n"
"tjänst kommando:\n"
"service_show/1 argument:\n"
"HTTP/ipa.example.com ----------------------\n"
"-----------------\n"
"---\n"

