msgstr ""
"\n"
" Ta bort ett villkor från regeln:\n"
"ipa automember-remove-condition --key=fqdn --type=hostgroup --inclusive-"
"regex=^web[1-9]+\\.example\\.com webserver\n"
"s\n"

