msgstr ""
"\n"
" Ta bort standardmålgruppen (fallback): ipa\n"
"automember-default-group-remove --type=hostgroup ipa\n"
"automember-default-group-remove --type=group\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/automember.py:112
