"\n"
" Show the default (fallback) target group:\n"
"    ipa automember-default-group-show --type=hostgroup\n"
"    ipa automember-default-group-show --type=group\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
" Visa standardmålgruppen (fallback): ipa\n"
