"       s1, s2: [0 .. 59.999]        (seconds latitude/longitude)\n"
"       alt:    [-100000.00 .. 42849672.95] BY .01 (altitude in meters)\n"
"       siz, hp, vp: [0 .. 90000000.00] (size/precision in meters)\n"
"    See RFC 1876 for details"
