"[siz[\"m\"]\n"
"[hp[\"m\"]\n"
"[vp[\"m\"]]]]\" där: d1: [0 .. 90] (grader\n"
"latitud) d2: [0 .. 180] (grader longitud) m1,\n"
"m2: [0 .. 59] (minuter latitud/longitud) s1, s2: [0\n"
".. 59,999] (sekunder latitud/longitud) alt: [-100000,00\n"
".. 42849672,95] MED .01 (höjd i meter) siz, hp, vp: [0 ..\n"
"90000000,00] (storlek/precision i meter) Se RFC 1876\n"
"för mer information"

