#: ipaserver/plugins/host.py:74
msgid ""
"\n"
"Hosts/Machines\n"
"\n"
"A host represents a machine. It can be used in a number of contexts:\n"
"- service entries are associated with a host\n"
"- a host stores the host/ service principal\n"
"- a host can be used in Host-based Access Control (HBAC) rules\n"
"- every enrolled client generates a host entry\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Värdar/maskiner\n"
"\n"
"En värd representerar en maskin. Den kan användas i flera sammanhang: -\n"
"tjänsteposter är kopplade till en värd - en\n"
"värd lagrar värden/tjänsteprincipen - en värd\n"
"kan användas i regler för värdbaserad åtkomstkontroll (HBAC) -\n"
"varje registrerad klient genererar en värdpost\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/host.py:82
msgid ""
"\n"
"ENROLLMENT:\n"
"\n"
"There are three enrollment scenarios when enrolling a new client:\n"
"\n"
"1. You are enrolling as a full administrator. The host entry may exist\n"
"   or not. A full administrator is a member of the hostadmin role\n"
"   or the admins group.\n"
"2. You are enrolling as a limited administrator. The host must already\n"
"   exist. A limited administrator is a member a role with the\n"
"   Host Enrollment privilege.\n"
"3. The host has been created with a one-time password.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"REGISTRERING:\n"
"\n"
"Det finns tre registreringsscenarier när du registrerar en ny klient:\n"
"\n"
"1. Du registrerar dig som fullständig administratör. Värdposteringen kan\n"
"finnas eller inte. En fullständig administratör är medlem i rollen\n"
"hostadmin eller gruppen\n"
"admins. 2. Du registrerar dig som begränsad administratör. Värden måste\n"
"redan existera. En begränsad administratör är medlem i en roll\n"
"med behörigheten Värdregistrering.\n"
"3. Värden har skapats med ett engångslösenord.\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/host.py:94
msgid ""
"\n"
"RE-ENROLLMENT:\n"
"\n"
"Host that has been enrolled at some point, and lost its configuration (e.g. "
"VM\n"
"destroyed) can be re-enrolled.\n"
"\n"
"For more information, consult the manual pages for ipa-client-install.\n"
"\n"
"A host can optionally store information such as where it is located,\n"
"the OS that it runs, etc.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"OMREGISTRERING:\n"
"\n"
"En värd som någon gång har registrerats och förlorat sin konfiguration "
"(t.ex. genom att\n"
"en virtuell maskin förstörts) kan\n"
"\n"
"registreras på nytt. Mer information finns i manualen för ipa-client-"
"install.\n"
"\n"
"En värd kan valfritt lagra information om t.ex. var den är placerad, vilket\n"
"operativsystem den kör osv.\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/host.py:106
msgid ""
"\n"
" Add a new host:\n"
"   ipa host-add --location=\"3rd floor lab\" --locality=Dallas test.example."
"com\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
" Lägg till en ny\n"
"värd: ipa host-add --location=\"3rd floor lab\" --locality=Dallas "
"test.example.co\n"
"m\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/host.py:109
msgid ""
"\n"
" Delete a host:\n"
"   ipa host-del test.example.com\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
" Ta bort en värd:\n"
