#: ipaserver/plugins/internal.py:1779
msgid ""
"<h1>Browser Kerberos Setup</h1>\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"<h1>Webbläsare Kerberos-inställningar</h1>\n"
"\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/internal.py:1783
msgid ""
"<h2>Firefox</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"            You can configure Firefox to use Kerberos for Single Sign-on. "
"The following instructions will guide you in configuring your web browser to "
"send your Kerberos credentials to the appropriate Key Distribution Center "
"which enables Single Sign-on.\n"
"</p>\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"<h2>Firefox</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"Du kan konfigurera Firefox för att använda Kerberos för enkel inloggning. "
"Följande instruktioner hjälper dig att konfigurera din webbläsare så att den "
"skickar dina Kerberos-inloggningsuppgifter till rätt "
"nyckeldistributionscenter, vilket möjliggör enkel inloggning.\n"
"</p>\n"
"\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/internal.py:1795
msgid ""
"<ol>\n"
"<li>\n"
"<p>\n"
"<a href=\"ca.crt\" id=\"ca-link\" class=\"btn btn-default\">Import "
"Certificate Authority certificate</a>\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Make sure you select <b>all three</b> checkboxes.\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                In the address bar of Firefox, type <code>about:config</"
"code> to display the list of current configuration options.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                In the Filter field, type <code>negotiate</code> to restrict "
"the list of options.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                Double-click the <code>network.negotiate-auth.trusted-uris</"
"code> entry to display the Enter string value dialog box.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                Enter the name of the domain against which you want to "
"authenticate, for example, <code class=\"example-domain\">.example.com</"
"code>.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li><a href=\"../ui/index.html\" id=\"return-link\" class=\"btn btn-"
"default\">Return to Web UI</a></li>\n"
"</ol>\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"<ol>\n"
"<li>\n"
"<p>\n"
"<a href=\"ca.crt\" id=\"ca-link\" class=\"btn-default\">Importera certifikat "
"från certifikatutfärdare</a>\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"Se till att du markerar <b>alla tre</b> kryssrutorna. </p> </li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"Skriv\n"
"<code>about:config</code>\n"
"i adressfältet i Firefox för att visa listan över aktuella "
"konfigurationsalternativ. </li> <li> Skriv <code>negotiate</code>\n"
"i\n"
"fältet\n"
"Filter för att begränsa listan med alternativ. </li> <li> Dubbelklicka på "
"posten\n"
"<cod\n"
"e>n\n"
"etwork.negotiate-auth.trusted-uris</code> för att visa dialogrutan Ange "
"strängvärde. </li> <li> Ange namnet på den domän som\n"
"du\n"
"vill\n"
"autentisera mot, till exempel <code class=\"example-domain\">.example.com</"
"code>. </li> <li><a href=\"../ui/index.html\" id=\"return-link\"\n"
"class=\"btn-default\">Återgå\n"
"till webbgränssnittet</a></li> </ol>\n"
"\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/internal.py:1831
msgid ""
"<h2>Chrome</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"            You can configure Chrome to use Kerberos for Single Sign-on. The "
"following instructions will guide you in configuring your web browser to "
"send your Kerberos credentials to the appropriate Key Distribution Center "
"which enables Single Sign-on.\n"
"</p>\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"<h2>Chrome</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"Du kan konfigurera Chrome för att använda Kerberos för enkel inloggning. "
"Följande instruktioner hjälper dig att konfigurera din webbläsare så att den "
"skickar dina Kerberos-inloggningsuppgifter till rätt "
"nyckeldistributionscenter, vilket möjliggör enkel inloggning.\n"
"</p>\n"
"\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/internal.py:1843
msgid ""
"<h3>Import CA Certificate</h3>\n"
"<ol>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                Download the <a href=\"ca.crt\">CA certificate</a>. "
"Alternatively, if the host is also an IdM client, you can find the "
"certificate in /etc/ipa/ca.crt.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                Click the menu button with the <em>Customize and control "
"Google Chrome</em> tooltip, which is by default in the top right-hand corner "
"of Chrome, and click <em>Settings</em>.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                Click <em>Show advanced settings</em> to display more "
"options, and then click the <em>Manage certificates</em> button located "
"under the HTTPS/SSL heading.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                In the <em>Authorities</em> tab, click the <em>Import</em> "
"button at the bottom.\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>Select the CA certificate file that you downloaded in the first step.</"
"li>\n"
"</ol>\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"<h3>Importera CA-certifikat</h3>\n"
"<ol>\n"
"<li>\n"
"Ladda ner <a href=\"ca.crt\">CA-certifikatet</a>. Alternativt, om värden "
"också är en IdM-klient, kan du hitta certifikatet i /etc/ipa/ca.crt. </li> "
"<li>\n"
"Klicka\n"
"på\n"
"menyknappen med verktygstipsets <em>Anpassa och kontrollera Google Chrome</"
"em>, som standard finns i det övre högra hörnet av Chrome, och klicka på <em>"
"Inställningar</em>. </li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"Klicka\n"
"på <em>Visa avancerade inställningar</em> för att visa fler alternativ och "
"klicka sedan på knappen <em>Hantera certifikat</em> under rubriken HTTPS/"
"SSL. </li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"Klicka\n"
"på knappen <em>Importera</em> längst ned på fliken <em>Myndigheter</em>. </"
"li> <li>Välj den\n"
"CA-certifikatfil\n"
"som du laddade ner i det första steget.</li> </ol>\n"
"\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/internal.py:1872
msgid ""
"<h3>\n"
"            Enable SPNEGO (Simple and Protected GSSAPI Negotiation "
"Mechanism) to Use Kerberos Authentication\n"
"            in Chrome\n"
"</h3>\n"
"<ol>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                Make sure you have the necessary directory created by "
"running:\n"
"<div><code>\n"
"                    [root@client]# mkdir -p /etc/opt/chrome/policies/"
"managed/\n"
"</code></div>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li>\n"
"                Create a new <code>/etc/opt/chrome/policies/managed/mydomain."
"json</code> file with write privileges limited to the system administrator "
"or root, and include the following line:\n"
"<div><code>\n"
"                    { \"AuthServerWhitelist\": \"*<span class=\"example-"
"domain\">.example.com</span>\" }\n"
"</code></div>\n"
"<div>\n"
"                    You can do this by running:\n"
"</div>\n"
"<div><code>\n"
"                    [root@server]# echo '{ \"AuthServerWhitelist\": \"*<span "
"class=\"example-domain\">.example.com</span>\" }' > /etc/opt/chrome/policies/"
"managed/mydomain.json\n"
"</code></div>\n"
"</li>\n"
"</ol>\n"
"<ol>\n"
"<p>\n"
"<strong>Note:</strong> If using Chromium, use <code>/etc/chromium/policies/"
"managed/</code> instead of <code>/etc/opt/chrome/policies/managed/</code> "
"for the two SPNEGO Chrome configuration steps above.\n"
"</p>\n"
"</ol>\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"<h3>\n"
"Aktivera SPNEGO (Simple and Protected GSSAPI Negotiation Mechanism) för att "
"använda Kerberos-autentisering\n"
"i Chrome </h3> <ol>\n"
"<li>\n"
"Se\n"
"till\n"
"att du har skapat den nödvändiga katalogen genom att köra: <div><code>\n"
"[root@client]#\n"
"mkdir -p /etc/opt/chrome/policies/managed/ </code></div> </li> <li> Skapa\n"
"en ny fil\n"
"<cod\n"
"e>/\n"
"etc/opt/chrome/policies/managed/mydomain.json</code> med skrivbehörighet "
"begränsad till systemadministratören eller root, och inkludera följande rad: "
"<div><code> { \"AuthServerWhitelist\":\n"
"\"*<span\n"
"class=\"example-domain\">.example.com</span>\" } </code></div> <div> Du kan "
"göra detta genom\n"
"att köra:\n"
"</div>\n"
"<div><code> [root@server]# echo '{\n"
"\"AuthServerWhitelist\":\n"
"\"*<span\n"
"class=\"example-domain\">.example.com</span>\" }' &gt; /etc/opt/chrome/"
"policies/managed/mydomain.json </code></div> </li> </ol> <ol> <p> <strong>"
"Obs!</strong>\n"
"Om du använder\n"
"Chromium,\n"
"använd\n"
"<co\n"
"de\n"
">/etc/chromium/policies/managed/</code> istället för <code>/etc/opt/chrome/"
"policies/managed/</code> för de två SPNEGO Chrome-konfigurationsstegen ovan. "
"</p> </ol>\n"
"\n"

#: ipaserver/plugins/internal.py:1917
msgid ""
"<h2>Internet Explorer</h2>\n"
"<p><strong>WARNING:</strong> Internet Explorer is no longer a supported "
"browser.</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"            Once you are able to log into the workstation with your kerberos "
"key you are now able to use that ticket in Internet Explorer.\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<h2>Internet Explorer</h2>\n"
"<p><strong>VARNING:</strong> Internet Explorer är inte längre en webbläsare "
"som stöds.</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
" När du har loggat in på arbetsstationen med din Kerberos-nyckel kan du nu "
"använda den biljetten i Internet Explorer.\n"
"</p>\n"
